So we can blend, scale, and
size with animal welfare.

00:29:40.865 --> 00:29:46.100 align:middle line:90%


00:29:46.100 --> 00:29:49.430 align:middle line:84%
>> John Brunnquell has succeeded
in improving the well-being

00:29:49.430 --> 00:29:52.430 align:middle line:84%
of his chickens while providing
eggs for the breakfasts

00:29:52.430 --> 00:29:55.040 align:middle line:90%
of 5,000 Americans every day.

00:29:55.040 --> 00:29:58.790 align:middle line:84%
But he has two problems
left to resolve.

00:29:58.790 --> 00:30:02.630 align:middle line:84%
The end of his hens' lives who,
after a year and a half when

00:30:02.630 --> 00:30:05.960 align:middle line:84%
they no longer lay enough eggs,
will be slaughtered and go

00:30:05.960 --> 00:30:09.260 align:middle line:90%
into the food chain.

00:30:09.260 --> 00:30:11.150 align:middle line:84%
And the beginning
of their lives.

00:30:11.150 --> 00:30:13.790 align:middle line:90%


00:30:13.790 --> 00:30:15.800 align:middle line:84%
>> Where do they come
from, the chicks?

00:30:15.800 --> 00:30:18.710 align:middle line:84%
>> We will buy day-old
chicks from the hatchery,

00:30:18.710 --> 00:30:21.300 align:middle line:84%
and then that's when we will
start taking over and managing

00:30:21.300 --> 00:30:22.100 align:middle line:90%
the bird.

00:30:22.100 --> 00:30:28.740 align:middle line:90%


00:30:28.740 --> 00:30:31.590 align:middle line:84%
>> This is actually a kind of
link in the supply chain that

00:30:31.590 --> 00:30:33.690 align:middle line:90%
is rarely talked about.

00:30:33.690 --> 00:30:36.570 align:middle line:84%
Hatcheries, of
course, you don't know

00:30:36.570 --> 00:30:42.240 align:middle line:84%
whether you're getting a male
or a female upon hatching.

00:30:42.240 --> 00:30:46.920 align:middle line:84%
They employ very highly
skilled individuals

00:30:46.920 --> 00:30:47.940 align:middle line:90%
called chicken sexers.

00:30:47.940 --> 00:30:49.085 align:middle line:90%
It's very hard to tell.

00:30:49.085 --> 00:30:50.460 align:middle line:84%
It's very hard to
pick up a chick

00:30:50.460 --> 00:30:52.652 align:middle line:84%
