male or a female.

00:30:52.652 --> 00:30:55.110 align:middle line:84%
And what these chicken sexers
do, of course, if it's a hen,

00:30:55.110 --> 00:30:57.720 align:middle line:84%
they will put it
in the keep box.

00:30:57.720 --> 00:31:00.570 align:middle line:84%
And if it's a male,
usually these males

00:31:00.570 --> 00:31:03.340 align:middle line:84%
are thrown into a grinder
or into a bag where

00:31:03.340 --> 00:31:04.140 align:middle line:90%
they suffocate.

00:31:04.140 --> 00:31:05.640 align:middle line:84%
Or in some cases,
they will just gas

00:31:05.640 --> 00:31:08.475 align:middle line:90%
a bunch of the male chickens.

00:31:08.475 --> 00:31:15.960 align:middle line:84%
A hatchery might produce,
in a day, 50,000 chickens.

00:31:15.960 --> 00:31:20.938 align:middle line:84%
Half of them, so yeah, 10,000,
20,000 a day are being killed.

00:31:20.938 --> 00:31:23.368 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:31:23.368 --> 00:31:33.580 align:middle line:90%


00:31:33.580 --> 00:31:35.320 align:middle line:90%
>> Not everything is perfect.

00:31:35.320 --> 00:31:38.300 align:middle line:84%
But when I see John
Brunnquell's chickens,

00:31:38.300 --> 00:31:40.210 align:middle line:84%
I think it is still
possible to change

00:31:40.210 --> 00:31:42.520 align:middle line:90%
the system from the inside.

00:31:42.520 --> 00:31:44.125 align:middle line:84%
Will many of them
be able to succeed?

00:31:44.125 --> 00:31:47.080 align:middle line:90%


00:31:47.080 --> 00:31:50.560 align:middle line:84%
There are already those who are
resisting industrialization,

00:31:50.560 --> 00:31:53.710 align:middle line:84%
happy to live well without
trying to get rich.

00:31:53.710 --> 00:31:58.273 align:middle line:84%
These are cow, pigs, and chicken
breeders, but also fisherman.

00:31:58.273 --> 00:32:02.140 align:middle line:90%


00:32:02.140 --> 00:32:05.350 align:middle line:84%
In the fishing industry,
industrialization has also

00:32:05.350 --> 00:32:08.650 align:middle line:90%
had a considerable impact.

00:32:08.650 --> 00:32:11.380 align:middle line:84%
The nets or trawlers
that scrape the seabed

00:32:11.380 --> 00:32:14.050 align:middle line:84%
to collect the fish that
ends up on our plates

00:32:14.050 --> 00:32:16.150 align:middle line:84%
kill animals which
are then immediately

00:32:16.150 --> 00:32:19.400 align:middle line:90%
thrown back into the sea.

00:32:19.400 --> 00:32:21.860 align:middle line:84%
At least 10 million
tons of marine animals

00:32:21.860 --> 00:32:26.510 align:middle line:84%
are killed each year as bycatch,
including turtles, dolphins,

00:32:26.510 --> 00:32:29.370 align:middle line:90%
and whales.

00:32:29.370 --> 00:32:31.110 align:middle line:84%
Imagine if the
label of a product

00:32:31.110 --> 00:32:33.330 align:middle line:84%
showed how many
animals were killed

00:32:33.330 --> 00:32:35.230 align:middle line:90%
so that you could eat it.

00:32:35.230 --> 00:32:39.400 align:middle line:84%
For example, for 500 grams
of prawns from Indonesia,

00:32:39.400 --> 00:32:43.380 align:middle line:84%
12 kilograms of other
marine animals were killed.

00:32:43.380 --> 00:32:45.930 align:middle line:84%
In order to eat tuna
sushi, you should

00:32:45.930 --> 00:32:50.550 align:middle line:84%
know that 145 other species
regularly die in the nets.

00:32:50.550 --> 00:32:53.650 align:middle line:90%


00:32:53.650 --> 00:32:56.710 align:middle line:84%
The situation is no
better in fish farms.

00:32:56.710 --> 00:32:59.800 align:middle line:84%
Because of overcrowding and
the poor quality of the water,

00:32:59.800 --> 00:33:03.880 align:middle line:84%
the mortality rates of
the fish can reach 30%.

00:33:03.880 --> 00:33:07.030 align:middle line:84%
But above all, to
feed the farmed fish,

00:33:07.030 --> 00:33:09.400 align:middle line:90%
we have to fish even more.

00:33:09.400 --> 00:33:13.030 align:middle line:84%
It takes 2 to 5 kilograms
of wild fish processed

00:33:13.030 --> 00:33:16.550 align:middle line:84%
into bone meal to feed 1
kilogram of farmed fish.

00:33:16.550 --> 00:33:28.380 align:middle line:90%


00:33:28.380 --> 00:33:31.080 align:middle line:84%
But here too, men and
women are refusing

00:33:31.080 --> 00:33:32.880 align:middle line:84%
to give in to the
call of expansion.

