00:38:42.130 --> 00:38:44.500 align:middle line:84%
We should also ask,
what kind of planet

00:38:44.500 --> 00:38:45.640 align:middle line:90%
do we want to leave them?

00:38:45.640 --> 00:38:49.340 align:middle line:90%


00:38:49.340 --> 00:38:51.890 align:middle line:84%
With 7 and 1/2 billion
people on earth,

00:38:51.890 --> 00:38:54.350 align:middle line:84%
meat and fish
consumption is excessive

00:38:54.350 --> 00:38:56.000 align:middle line:84%
and has become a
serious problem.

00:38:56.000 --> 00:38:58.970 align:middle line:90%


00:38:58.970 --> 00:39:01.490 align:middle line:84%
To produce the animals
that we eat today,

00:39:01.490 --> 00:39:06.213 align:middle line:84%
we are damaging the world
they will grow up in tomorrow.

00:39:06.213 --> 00:39:07.880 align:middle line:84%
>> I mean, the numbers
are pretty clear,

00:39:07.880 --> 00:39:12.440 align:middle line:84%
