00:39:20.910 --> 00:39:24.290 align:middle line:84%
And that's a kind
of remarkable chunk

00:39:24.290 --> 00:39:29.078 align:middle line:84%
of responsibility for just one
industry in the global economy.

00:39:29.078 --> 00:39:39.073 align:middle line:90%


00:39:39.073 --> 00:39:40.490 align:middle line:84%
It's safe to say
that if we didn't

00:39:40.490 --> 00:39:42.490 align:middle line:84%
have industrial and
