00:40:01.580 --> 00:40:03.312 align:middle line:84%
to kind of put that
in perspective.

00:40:03.312 --> 00:40:06.410 align:middle line:90%


00:40:06.410 --> 00:40:08.870 align:middle line:84%
>> To face the rising
