00:40:12.789 --> 00:40:21.771 align:middle line:90%


00:40:21.771 --> 00:40:24.290 align:middle line:90%
>> [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH]

00:40:24.290 --> 00:40:46.730 align:middle line:90%


00:40:46.730 --> 00:40:50.300 align:middle line:84%
>> To fatten up the billions of
animals as quickly as possible

00:40:50.300 --> 00:40:53.870 align:middle line:84%
