destroy forests,

00:40:58.160 --> 00:41:01.610 align:middle line:84%
which increases global warming
and destroys biodiversity.

00:41:01.610 --> 00:41:06.470 align:middle line:90%


00:41:06.470 --> 00:41:09.410 align:middle line:84%
The quantity of water
required for these crops,

00:41:09.410 --> 00:41:14.610 align:middle line:84%
