00:41:14.610 --> 00:41:17.400 align:middle line:84%
And the huge quantities
of pesticides and chemical

00:41:17.400 --> 00:41:20.580 align:middle line:84%
fertilizers that we
apply destroy the soil

00:41:20.580 --> 00:41:23.394 align:middle line:90%
and endangers our health.

